description._content: Description: Begonia grown at the Botanic Station. Location: Seychelles Date: 1900-1929 Description: Entrance to Court House, 9th November, 1903. Police guard of honour in distance. Location: Seychelles Date: 09 November 1903 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/771 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
